InputEnum - Enum in org.lfenergy.operatorfabric.cards.model
The type of input TEXTThis input will be displayed as an input text LISTThis input will be displayed as a dropbox MULTI_LISTThis input will be displayed as multivalued list input SWITCH_LISTThis input is displayed as two list whose values may be exchanged LONG_TEXTThis input will be displayed as a multi line input text BOOLEANThis input will be displayed as a boolean STATICThis input won't be displayed, it may serve as a constant parameter Note : This enum is created by hand because Swagger can't handle enums.

Recipient - Class in org.lfenergy.operatorfabric.cards.model
Recipient object defines rules for recipient computation
Recipient() - Constructor for class org.lfenergy.operatorfabric.cards.model.Recipient
 
RecipientEnum - Enum in org.lfenergy.operatorfabric.cards.model
Recipient type enumeration BROADCASTCard is sent to everyone DEADENDCard is sent to no one (Mostly for testing purposes) GROUPCard is sent to a whole group TSODeprecated alias for GROUP UNIONCard is sent to the union of underlying recipients INTERSECTCard is sent to the intersection of underlying recipients USERCard is sent to a specified user FAVORITECard is sent to underlying recipient, if favorite specified user is available, it is set as main recipient RANDOMCard is sent to underlying recipient, a main recipient is randomly set WEIGHTEDCard is sent to underlying recipient, a main recipient is randomly set but a specified user is favored Note : This enum is created by hand because Swagger can't handle enums.
